"title": "5016: heart, fallen and redeemed",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5016",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The inner thoughts and feelings of an unregenerate person are opposed to God, making that person reject God and his love. At conversion the renewing work of the Holy Spirit transforms the human heart, enabling it to love and obey God.</p>\n<h2>The unregenerate heart</h2>\n<h3>Hostile to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:1\">PSA 14:1</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps53:1\">PSA 53:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:3\">1KI 15:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:14\">2CH 12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:3\">PRO 19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:42\">JHN 5:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:21-Acts8:22\">ACT 8:21–8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:31\">ROM 1:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:7\">ROM 8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:12\">HEB 3:12</a></p>\n<h3>Hardened against God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:12\">JER 18:12</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:21\">EXO 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:3\">EXO 7:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:14\">EXO 7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:22-Exod7:23\">EXO 7:22–7:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:15\">EXO 8:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:32\">EXO 8:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:8\">EXO 14:8</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut2:30\">DEU 2:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:10\">ISA 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:25\">ISA 42:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:12\">JER 16:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:20\">DAN 5:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:15\">MAT 13:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:27\">ACT 28:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:5\">ROM 2:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:9\">REV 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:11\">REV 16:11</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritually ignorant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:18\">EPH 4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam6:16\">2SA 6:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr15:29\">1CH 15:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21\">ROM 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:15\">2CO 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>Proud</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:7\">PSA 73:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:12\">PRO 18:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:4\">PRO 21:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:29\">JER 48:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:16\">JER 49:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:2\">EZK 28:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek28:17\">EZK 28:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:3\">OBA 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:7\">REV 18:7</a></p>\n<h3>Deceitful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:9\">JER 17:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:33-Job31:34\">JOB 31:33–31:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps5:9\">PSA 5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps28:3\">PSA 28:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:4\">PSA 62:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:14\">PRO 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:7\">PRO 23:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:12\">PRO 24:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:23-Prov26:25\">PRO 26:23–26:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:20\">ISA 44:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:17\">JER 22:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:13\">2TI 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Sinful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5\">GEN 6:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:13\">JOB 36:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:3\">PSA 10:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:6\">PSA 41:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:21\">PSA 55:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:18\">PRO 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:9\">PRO 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:5\">ISA 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:4\">MAT 9:4</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:8\">MRK 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:22\">LUK 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:18-Matt15:19\">MAT 15:18–15:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:20-Mark7:23\">MRK 7:20–7:23</a></p>\n<h3>Condemned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:20\">PRO 11:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps101:4-Ps101:5\">PSA 101:4–101:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:5\">PRO 16:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:20\">PRO 17:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:9\">ECC 11:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:12\">ISA 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:10\">JER 17:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek25:6-Ezek25:7\">EZK 25:6–25:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:24\">ROM 1:24</a></p>\n<h2>Conversion: the changed heart</h2>\n<h3>Convinced of need</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:8\">JHN 16:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:12-Jer29:14\">JER 29:12–29:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:37\">ACT 2:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:30\">ACT 16:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:7\">ROM 7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:25\">1CO 14:25</a></p>\n<h3>Changed by the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:25-Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:25–36:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:14\">JER 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:7\">JER 24:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:19\">EZK 11:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:31\">EZK 18:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:5-John3:6\">JHN 3:5–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:29\">ROM 2:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:4-Titus3:5\">TIT 3:4–3:5</a></p>\n<h3>Given faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:6\">2CO 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:31-Acts5:32\">ACT 5:31–5:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:9\">ACT 15:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:14-Acts16:15\">ACT 16:14–16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:8-Rom10:10\">ROM 10:8–10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8\">EPH 2:8</a></p>\n<h2>Spurious conversion</h2>\n<h3>A less-than-saving change</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:9\">1SA 10:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:5-Matt13:6\">MAT 13:5–13:6</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:5-Mark4:6\">MRK 4:5–4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:6\">LUK 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:20-Matt13:21\">MAT 13:20–13:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:16-Mark4:17\">MRK 4:16–4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:13\">LUK 8:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4-Heb6:8\">HEB 6:4–6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:26-Heb10:29\">HEB 10:26–10:29</a></p>",
